    <title>Python Data Science Handbook 读书笔记 Numpy 篇</title>
    <url>/2021/02/23/PythonDataScienceHandbook-Numpy/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Numpy-入门"><a href="#Numpy-入门" class="headerlink" title="Numpy 入门"></a>Numpy 入门</h1><p>Numpy 牺牲了一些灵活性，采用了固定类型的数组来高效地储存和运算。</p>
<figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> numpy <span class="keyword">as</span> np</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>不同于 Python lists，Numpy array 中所有元素都具有相同类型。</p>
<figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 强制类型转换</span></span><br><span class="line">np.array([<span class="number">3.14</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>])</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">array([ 3.14,  4.  ,  2.  ,  3.  ])</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 制定Numpy变量类型</span></span><br><span class="line">np.array([<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>], dtype=<span class="string">&#x27;float32&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">array([ 1.,  2.,  3.,  4.], dtype=float32)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


<h2 id="创建-Numpy-array"><a href="#创建-Numpy-array" class="headerlink" title="创建 Numpy array"></a>创建 Numpy array</h2><ol>
<li>将 Python list 转化为 Numpy array</li>
<li>利用函数构造 Numpy array，这对大型数组来说效率较高</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 嵌套列表转化为高维数组</span></span><br><span class="line">np.array([<span class="built_in">range</span>(i, i + <span class="number">3</span>) <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> [<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">6</span>]])</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">array([[2, 3, 4],</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">       [4, 5, 6],</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">       [6, 7, 8]])</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 几个常用的函数</span></span><br><span class="line">np.zeros()</span><br><span class="line">np.ones()</span><br><span class="line">np.full()</span><br><span class="line">np.empty()</span><br><span class="line">np.eye()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">np.arange()</span><br><span class="line">np.linspace()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">np.random.random()</span><br><span class="line">np.random.normal()</span><br><span class="line">np.random.randint()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="指定-Numpy-数据类型"><a href="#指定-Numpy-数据类型" class="headerlink" title="指定 Numpy 数据类型"></a>指定 Numpy 数据类型</h2><ol>
<li>使用 str 指定，<code>np.zeros(10, dtype=&#39;int16&#39;)</code></li>
<li>使用 Numpy 对象也可，<code>np.zeros(10, dtype=np.int16)</code></li>
</ol>
<p>Numpy 标准数据类型详见<a class="link"   href="https://numpy.org/" >Numpy documentation<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a>。</p>
<h1 id="Numpy-array-属性"><a href="#Numpy-array-属性" class="headerlink" title="Numpy array 属性"></a>Numpy array 属性</h1><p>几个比较重要的属性</p>
<ol>
<li><code>ndim</code>，维度数量</li>
<li><code>shape</code>，形状</li>
<li><code>size</code>，元素数量</li>
<li><code>dtype</code>，数据类型</li>
</ol>
<p>除此之外还有</p>
<ol>
<li><code>itemsize</code>，size in byte</li>
<li><code>nbyte</code>，total size in byte</li>
</ol>
<h1 id="基础操作"><a href="#基础操作" class="headerlink" title="基础操作"></a>基础操作</h1><h2 id="Indexing"><a href="#Indexing" class="headerlink" title="Indexing"></a>Indexing</h2><p>在获取数组中的单个元素时，Numpy array 和 Python list 的操作方式几乎相同。</p>
<ol>
<li>从0开始，负数表示从末尾开始</li>
<li>高维数组逗号分隔</li>
<li>修改时注意强制类型转换</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 一维数组</span></span><br><span class="line">x = np.array([<span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">7</span>, <span class="number">9</span>])</span><br><span class="line">x[<span class="number">0</span>] <span class="comment"># 从零开始</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">5</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">x[-<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="comment"># 可以倒着来</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">9</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 二维数组</span></span><br><span class="line">x = np.array(</span><br><span class="line">    [[<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">4</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="number">7</span>, <span class="number">6</span>, <span class="number">8</span>, <span class="number">8</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">6</span>, <span class="number">7</span>, <span class="number">7</span>]])</span><br><span class="line">x[<span class="number">2</span>,<span class="number">0</span>] <span class="comment"># 注意shape</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">x[<span class="number">2</span>,-<span class="number">1</span>] <span class="comment"># 同样可以倒着来</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">7</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 可以直接修改，需要注意强制类型转换</span></span><br><span class="line">x[<span class="number">2</span>,-<span class="number">1</span>] = <span class="number">8</span></span><br><span class="line">x</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">array([[12,  5,  2,  4],</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">       [ 7,  6,  8,  8],</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">       [ 1,  6,  7,  8]])</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Slicing"><a href="#Slicing" class="headerlink" title="Slicing"></a>Slicing</h2><p>同样类似 Python list，遵循着 <code>x[start: stop: step]</code>，它们的默认值是：</p>
<ul>
<li><code>start = 0</code></li>
<li><code>stop = size of demension</code></li>
<li><code>step = 1</code></li>
</ul>
<p>注意 <code>step</code> 为负数的时候会将数组反转。</p>
<figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x = np.array(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">6</span>, <span class="number">7</span>, <span class="number">8</span>, <span class="number">9</span>])</span><br><span class="line">x[::<span class="number">2</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">array([0, 2, 4, 6, 8])</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">x[::-<span class="number">1</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">array([9, 8, 7, 6, 5, 4, 3, 2, 1, 0])</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">x[<span class="number">5</span>::-<span class="number">2</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">array([5, 3, 1])</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">x = np.array(</span><br><span class="line">    [[<span class="number">12</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">4</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="number">7</span>, <span class="number">6</span>, <span class="number">8</span>, <span class="number">8</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">6</span>, <span class="number">7</span>, <span class="number">7</span>]])</span><br><span class="line">x[:<span class="number">2</span>, :<span class="number">3</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">array([[12,  5,  2],</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">       [ 7,  6,  8]])</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">print(x[:, <span class="number">0</span>])</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">[12  7  1]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">print(x2[<span class="number">0</span>, :])</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">[12  5  2  4]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>和 Python list 不同，Numpy array 切片返回的是 <em>views</em>，不是 <em>copies</em>。修改 <em>views</em> 会同时修改原数组，而修改 <em>copies</em> 则不会。</p>
<figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span><span class="keyword">import</span> numpy <span class="keyword">as</span> np</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x = np.random.randint(<span class="number">10</span>, size=(<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>))</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x</span><br><span class="line">array([[<span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">7</span>, <span class="number">2</span>],</span><br><span class="line">       [<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">7</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">1</span>],</span><br><span class="line">       [<span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">2</span>]])</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x_sub = x[:<span class="number">2</span>, :<span class="number">2</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x_sub</span><br><span class="line">array([[<span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">4</span>],</span><br><span class="line">       [<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">7</span>]])</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x_sub[<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">0</span>] = <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x_sub</span><br><span class="line">array([[<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">4</span>],</span><br><span class="line">       [<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">7</span>]])</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x</span><br><span class="line">array([[<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">7</span>, <span class="number">2</span>],</span><br><span class="line">       [<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">7</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">1</span>],</span><br><span class="line">       [<span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">2</span>]])</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x_sub_copy = x[:<span class="number">2</span>, :<span class="number">2</span>].copy()</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x_sub_copy</span><br><span class="line">array([[<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">4</span>],</span><br><span class="line">       [<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">7</span>]])</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x_sub_copy[<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>] = <span class="number">9</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x_sub_copy</span><br><span class="line">array([[<span class="number">9</span>, <span class="number">4</span>],</span><br><span class="line">       [<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">7</span>]])</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;&gt;&gt; </span>x</span><br><span class="line">array([[<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">7</span>, <span class="number">2</span>],</span><br><span class="line">       [<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">7</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">1</span>],</span><br><span class="line">       [<span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">2</span>]])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Reshape"><a href="#Reshape" class="headerlink" title="Reshape"></a>Reshape</h2><h2 id="Concatenation-amp-splitting"><a href="#Concatenation-amp-splitting" class="headerlink" title="Concatenation &amp; splitting"></a>Concatenation &amp; splitting</h2>]]></content>
